Bio-Community version 0.01
==========================

THIS MODULE IS IN EARLY DEVELOPMENT STAGE! VERY LITTLE IS USEABLE RIGHT NOW AND
IT IS PROBABLY BUG-RIDDEN!

Bio::Community is a BioPerl-based module to represent and manipulate communities
of organisms. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  BioPerl version >= 1.006902
  Moose
  Moose::Util::TypeConstraints
  MooseX::NonMoose
  MooseX::Method::Signatures
  Test::Number::Delta

